title: Episode 23 - Catharine Pendrel Interview
itunes:title: Episode 23 - Catharine Pendrel Interview
description: Today we talk to Catharine Pendrel, the Canadian Bronze Medalist in Women's Cross Country Mountain Biking from the 2016 Rio Olympics. Catharine chats to use about her entire Olympic journey, from her exciting debut performance in Beijing 2008, the disappointment following the 2012 London Games, and just how close the dramatic race to the finish was in Rio against her Canadian team mate. We also get Catharine's answers to the famous Team Canada "Hi, My Name Is" questionnaire.
